{"title_page": "1958\u201359 Norwegian Main League", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition        = [[Eliteserien|Hovedserien]]\n| season             = 1958\u201359\n| winners            = [[Lillestr\u00f8m SK|Lillestr\u00f8m]]<br />1st title\n| relegated          = [[Asker Fotball|Asker]]<br>[[\u00c5rstad IL|\u00c5rstad]]<br>[[SK Freidig|Freidig]]<br>[[Kapp IF|Kapp]]\n| matches            = \n| total goals        = \n| highest attendance = \n| lowest attendance  = \n| average attendance = \n| prevseason         = [[1957\u201358 Norwegian Main League|1957\u201358]]\n| nextseason         = [[1959\u201360 Norwegian Main League|1959\u201360]]\n}}\nThe '''1958\u20131959 [[Eliteserien|Hovedserien]]''' was the 14th completed season of top division [[association football|football]] in [[Norway]].\n\n==Overview==\nIt was contested by 16 teams, and [[Lillestr\u00f8m SK|Lillestr\u00f8m]] won the championship, their first league title.\n\n==Teams and locations==\n:''Note: Table lists in alphabetical order.\n{| border=\"0\"\n| valign=\"top\" |\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\"\n|+Group A\n|-\n! Team\n!{{Tooltip| Ap. | Appearances in top divisions of Norwegian football}}\n! Location\n|-\n| [[\u00c5rstad IL|\u00c5rstad]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''7'''\n| [[Bergen]]\n|-\n| [[Asker Fotball|Asker]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''8'''\n| [[Asker]]\n|-\n| [[SK Brann|Brann]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''11'''\n| [[Bergen]]\n|-\n| [[Eik-T\u00f8nsberg|Eik]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''2'''\n| [[T\u00f8nsberg]]\n|-\n| [[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''14'''\n| [[Fredrikstad]]\n|-\n| [[Gre\u00e5ker IF|Gre\u00e5ker]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''1'''\n| [[Sarpsborg]]\n|-\n| [[Sandefjord BK]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''13'''\n| [[Sandefjord]]\n|-\n| [[Viking FK|Viking]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''14'''\n| [[Stavanger]]\n|}\n| valign=\"top\" |\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\"\n|+Group B\n|-\n! Team\n!{{Tooltip| Ap. | Appearances in top divisions of 