 seasons]]\n[[Category:1959\u201360 in European association football leagues|Norway]]\n[[Category:1959 in Norwegian football]]\n[[Category:1960 in Norwegian football]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition        = [[Eliteserien|Hovedserien]]\n| season             = 1959\u201360\n| winners            = [[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]]<br />8th title\n| relegated          = [[SK Brann|Brann]]<br>[[IK Start|Start]]<br>[[Raufoss Fotball|Raufoss]]<br>[[SK Brage|Brage]]\n| continentalcup1    = [[1960\u201361 European Cup|European Cup]] \n| continentalcup1 qualifiers = Fredrikstad\n| matches            = \n| total goals        = \n| highest attendance = \n| lowest attendance  = \n| average attendance = \n| prevseason         = [[1958\u201359 Norwegian Main League|1958\u201359]]\n| nextseason         = [[1960\u201361 Norwegian Main League|1960\u201361]]\n}}\nThe '''1959\u20131960 [[Eliteserien|Hovedserien]]''' was the 15th completed season of top division [[association football|football]] in [[Norway]].\n\n==Overview==\nIt was contested by 16 teams, and [[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]] won the championship, their eighth league title. This was the first season a bronze medal was awarded.\n\n==Teams and locations==\n:''Note: Table lists in alphabetical order.\n{| border=\"0\"\n| valign=\"top\" |\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\"\n|+Group A\n|-\n! Team\n!{{Tooltip| Ap. | Appearances in top divisions of Norwegian football}}<!--Begins with 1937\u201338 season. Abandoned 1939\u201340 season does not count.-->\n! Location\n|-\n| [[SK Brann|Brann]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''12'''\n| [[Bergen]]\n|-\n| [[Gre\u00e5ker IF|Gre\u00e5ker]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''2'''\n| [[Sarpsborg]]\n|-\n| [[Larvik Turn & IF|Larvik Turn]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''11'''\n| [[Larvik]]\n|-\n| [[Lillestr\u00f8m SK|Lillestr\u00f8m]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''10'''\n| [[Lillestr\u00f8m]]\n|-\n| [[Sandefjord BK]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''14'''\n| [[Sandefjord]]\n|-\n| [[IK Start