uropean association football leagues|Norway]]\n[[Category:1960 in Norwegian football]]\n[[Category:1961 in Norwegian football]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition        = [[Eliteserien|Hovedserien]]\n| season             = 1960\u201361\n| winners            = [[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]]<br />9th title\n| relegated          = [[Str\u00f8mmen IF|Str\u00f8mmen]]<br>[[Stavanger IF Fotball|Stavanger]]<br>[[Lillestr\u00f8m SK|Lillestr\u00f8m]]<br>[[SK Rapid|Rapid]]\n| continentalcup1    = [[1961\u201362 European Cup|European Cup]]           \n| continentalcup1 qualifiers = Fredrikstad\n| matches            = \n| total goals        = \n| highest attendance = \n| lowest attendance  = \n| average attendance = \n| prevseason         = [[1959\u201360 Norwegian Main League|1959\u201360]]\n| nextseason         = [[1961\u201362 Norwegian Main League|1961\u201362]]\n}}\nThe '''1960\u20131961 [[Eliteserien|Hovedserien]]''' was the 16th completed season of top division [[association football|football]] in [[Norway]].\n\n==Overview==\nIt was contested by 16 teams, and [[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]] won the championship, their second consecutive league title and ninth title overall.\n\n==Teams and locations==\n:''Note: Table lists in alphabetical order.\n{| border=\"0\"\n| valign=\"top\" |\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\"\n|+Group A\n|-\n! Team\n!{{Tooltip| Ap. | Appearances in top divisions of Norwegian football}}\n! Location\n|-\n| [[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''16'''\n| [[Fredrikstad]]\n|-\n| [[Larvik Turn & IF|Larvik Turn]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''12'''\n| [[Larvik]]\n|-\n| [[Odds BK|Odd]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''14'''\n| [[Skien]]\n|-\n| [[Lisleby FK|Lisleby]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''5'''\n| [[Fredrikstad]]\n|-\n| [[Stavanger IF Fotball|Stavanger]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''4'''\n| [[Stavanger]]\n|-\n| [[Str\u00f8mmen IF|Str\u00f8mmen]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''11'''\n| [[Str\u00f8mmen]]\n|-\n| [[V\u00e5lerenga