gory:Films with screenplays by Neal Purvis and Robert Wade]]\n[[Category:Films with screenplays by Jez Butterworth]]\n", "name_user": "Percytown", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spectre_(2015_film)"}
